{"tid":1811363,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【行動和你Jam】觀塘1月6 號","createTime":"2020-01-04T15:36:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-06T04:25:17.000Z","uid":45858,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"d2a7911488802681277135a14a0f394c240a3320","tid":1811363,"uid":45858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T15:36:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SKgdzJ8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSKgdzJ8.jpg&h=14a8c0ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【和你Jam】<br />\n<br />\n日期：2020年1月6日（星期一）<br />\n時間：下午12:00-3:00<br />\n地點：觀塘巧明街/駿業街Walking East 雕塑<br />\n<br />\n香港保險仝人職工會 + 香港音樂人工會 招募會員聯合街站<br />\n<br />\n12月罷工試過同 香港酒店工會 Hong Kong Hotel Employees Union一起開站；1月6號我地又出動啦！今次選擇中午和你Jam，重要同 香港保險㒰人職工會 Hong Kong Insurance Union一齊落區開街站！各位保險人音樂人，中午放飯落來啦！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n香港保險仝人職工會TG頻道（附設公海）：<a href=\"https://t.me/hkiunion\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkiunion&d=x%2FFuRRgY0RqQB1T9iHKuLWINpH3PnqyTY83oYMeb7B8%3D&h=a5bc6d5d\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkiunion</a><br />\n登記成為「香港保險仝人職工會」會員：<a href=\"https://cutt.ly/reTxKIo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcutt.ly%2FreTxKIo&d=x%2FFuRRgY0RqQB1T9iHKuLWINpH3PnqyTY83oYMeb7B8%3D&h=ca262edd\" target=\"_blank\">https://cutt.ly/reTxKIo</a><br />\n<br />\n香港音樂人工會TG頻道（附設公海）：<a href=\"https://t.me/HKMuIN\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FHKMuIN&d=x%2FFuRRgY0RqQB1T9iHKuLWINpH3PnqyTY83oYMeb7B8%3D&h=5417d259\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/HKMuIN</a><br />\n登記成為「香港音樂人工會」會員：<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2NBwQHE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2NBwQHE&d=x%2FFuRRgY0RqQB1T9iHKuLWINpH3PnqyTY83oYMeb7B8%3D&h=cf2b7a27\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2NBwQHE</a><br />\n<br />\n#和你Jam<br />\n#工會街站<br />\n#香港